  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2013/12/11/valve-steam-mobile-ios-update/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/3d08d96e89e708020ad156ca55c54e2/steam-mobile-2013-12-11-01.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\nValve 在去年推出了 <a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2012/01/27/steam-beta-for-android-and-ios/\">Steam Mobile</a>，让用户无需通过电脑便可方便地在移动设备上购买游戏、保持在线。而在今天，这款应用的 iOS 版本迎来了升级，新版中专门针对 iOS 7 修改了 UI，同时还支持离线聊天，改进了推送通知。除此之外，好友界面也变得更简洁，邀请、昵称、Big Picture、行动状态、Facebook 好友推荐等内容都显示得更清楚了。当然，应用得稳定性和性能也都有所提升，有需要的朋友去饮用来源看看吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/11/valve-steam-mobile-ios-update/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://appadvice.com/appnn/2013/12/valves-steam-mobile-client-redesigned-for-ios-7-updated-with-improvements\" target=\"_blank\">AppAdvice.com</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/steam-mobile/id495369748\" target=\"_blank\">Valve (iTunes)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/11/valve-steam-mobile-ios-update/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20786317/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/11/valve-steam-mobile-ios-update/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
